es, the real fun begins. When she dons her hamster hoodie, she transforms from a refined, over-achieving student into a lazy, junk food-eating otaku, leaving all the housework to her responsible older brother Taihei. Whether she\'s hanging out with her friends Nana Ebina and Kirie Motoba, or competing with her self-proclaimed \"rival\" Sylphinford Tachibana, Umaru knows how to kick back and have some fun! Himouto! Umaru-chan is a cute story that follows the daily adventures of Umaru and Taihei, as they take care of—and put up with—each other the best they can, as well as the unbreakable bonds between friends and siblings. [Written by MAL Rewrite]',NULL,7.21,'TV','2015-07-09 07:00:00','2015-09-24 07:00:00','Jul 9, 2015 to Sep 24, 2015','flaskr/static/anime_cover_images/28825.jpg','https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/12/75086.jpg','https://www.youtube.com/embed/PJ10D-q8kLw?enablejsapi=1&wmode=opaque&autoplay=1'),(28835,'Tesagure! Bukatsumono Spin-off Purupurun Sharumu to Asobou',NULL,'てさぐれ！部活もの すぴんおふ プルプルんシャルムと遊ぼう',12,'Original',3430,13,'Finished Airing',3735,7205,1055,'23 min per ep','A spin-off of the Tesagure! Bukatsumono series.',NULL,6.96,'TV','2015-04-05 07:00:00','2015-06-28 07:00:00','Apr 5, 2015 to Jun 28, 2015','flaskr/static/anime_cover_images/28835.jpg','https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/9/72297.jpg','https://www.youtube.com/embed/-Nh_otTZhv8?enablejsapi=1&wmode=opaque&autoplay=1'),(28841,'Wake Up, Girls! Seishun no Kage',NULL,'Wake Up, Girls！青春の影',1,'Original',7709,8,'Finished Airing',2920,5203,2734,'54 min','Movie sequel of Wake Up, Girls!, announced at Wake Up, Girls! Festa.2014 Winter.',NULL,7.16,'Movie','2015-09-25 07:00:00',NULL,'Sep 25, 2015','flaskr/static/anime_cover_images/28841.jpg','https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/6/75337.jpg','https://www.youtube.com/embed/nWzUh717mNY?enablejsapi=1&wmode=opaque&autoplay=1'),(28853,'Pokemon: Pikachu to Pokemon Ongakutai','Pikachu and the Pokemon Music Squad','ポケモン・ザ・ムービーXY『ピカチュウとポケモンおんがくたい』